00:28:53.086 --> 00:28:54.187
Y...

00:28:57.296 --> 00:28:59.397
Nunca volveré a huir.

00:29:30.457 --> 00:29:31.556
Sr. Kang?

00:29:37.336 --> 00:29:39.036
Al menos deberías dormir cómodamente.

